', and can be heard on its original cast recording. He also appeared in the acclaimed Off-Broadway production of "End of the World Party", among his other New York stage credits.  <p>

He is well known to cinema audiences for his role as 'Vinnie' in the 1985 horror film , and as 'Vincent 'Alphabet' Longuilli', in the 1987 <conflict wordnetid="100958896" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
