Hamburger Hill</link></movie>
</it>, as well as his favorite film appearance - 'Warren' in <movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../357/6199357.xml">
Kiss Me, Guido</link></movie>
.</p>
